mstItem.name: Servant Coin
mstItem.detail:
"Servant Enhancement Material"
 A shard of a Servant's Spirit Origin

mstItem.name: Phoenix Feather
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
Feather from a sacred bird of the Orient.

mstItem.name: Seed of Yggdrasil
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A seed of a giant tree that symbolizes the world.

mstItem.name: Proof of Hero
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
Proof that you've been acknowledged as a hero.
Many possess it, but they aren't 
conscious of it so they forget.

mstItem.name: Aurora Steel
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A piece of divine steel that glistens like the flickering aurora.
The Valkyries from Norse mythology are said to have soared through the heavens wearing armor made of this steel.

mstItem.name: Secret Gem of Lancer
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up Material"
A bright stone glimmering with the immense power of a Lancer.

mstItem.name: Eternal Ice
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
Ice that does not melt, even at room temperature.
Some see a lovely crystalline flower, but those with no appreciation of beauty see only a piece of ice.

mstItem.name: Claw of Chaos
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
Those wounded by this claw become prisoners of chaos.

mstItem.name: Ghost Lantern
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
Lantern that uses souls as fuel to burn.

mstItem.name: Crystallized Lore
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A highly pure crystal of magic created
when human history crosses a stream of Mana.
It can be said that it is the ingredient for materializing Heroic Spirits.

mstItem.name: Gem of Lancer
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up Material"
A bright stone glimmering with the power of a Lancer.

mstItem.name: Lamp of Evil-Sealing
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A fascinating lamp that is said to
have sealed in an elemental
with tremendous magical energy.

mstItem.name: Heart of the Foreign God
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
The heart of a savage demi-god.
A god is a god, even if it's a fake.
Its heartbeat emits many curses.

mstItem.name: Holy Grail
mstItem.detail:
A container said to grant any wish.
Created by the Third Magic, it is said 
that it can materialize those that do not possess forms.

mstItem.name: Magic Gem of Lancer
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up Material"
A bright stone glimmering with the great power of a Lancer.

mstItem.name: Lancer Piece
mstItem.detail:
"Ascension Material"
A piece signifying the Lancer class.

mstItem.name: Lancer Monument
mstItem.detail:
"Ascension Material"
A monument in glory of the Lancer class.
